== 墓主 ==

秦东陵是个大的墓葬区，埋葬着[[悼太子_(秦国)|秦悼太子]]以后到[[秦始皇|秦始皇]]之前的[[秦昭襄王|昭襄王]]、[[秦孝文王|孝文王]]、[[秦莊襄王|庄襄王]]、[[宣太后|宣太后]]等著名人物。<ref>{{cite web|author=考古与文物|title=秦东陵刍议|url=http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=8&CurRec=2&recid=&filename=KGYW200003007&dbname=CJFD2000&dbcode=CJFQ&pr=&urlid=&yx=&v=MTQ0MTNJOUZZNFI4ZVgxTHV4WVM3RGgxVDNxVHJXTTFGckNVUkw2ZmIrWm9GeXZsVmJyTkxpclNlYkc0SHRITXI=|accessdate=2000年03期|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305012605/http://www.cnki.net/KCMS/detail/detail.aspx?QueryID=8&CurRec=2&recid=&filename=KGYW200003007&dbname=CJFD2000&dbcode=CJFQ&pr=&urlid=&yx=&v=MTQ0MTNJOUZZNFI4ZVgxTHV4WVM3RGgxVDNxVHJXTTFGckNVUkw2ZmIrWm9GeXZsVmJyTkxpclNlYkc0SHRITXI=|archivedate=2016-03-05}}</ref>

